      "definition": "<p><b>Headache</b> is the symptom of pain anywhere in the region of the head or neck, which can be classified as a <i>primary disorder</i> (e.g., migraine, tension, cluster) or as a <i>secondary symptom</i> of an underlying pathology (e.g., hemorrhage, tumor, infection).</p>",
