      "definition": "<p>The <b>Nervous System</b> is the body's primary communication and control network, divided into the Central Nervous System (CNS), consisting of the brain and spinal cord, and the Peripheral Nervous System (PNS), which includes all other nervous tissue. It is composed of specialized cells, primarily [[63fc3fe7|neurons]] and glial cells.</p>",
